-- ctrl S

ctrlS : 𝟚 ×ᵤ 𝟚 ×ᵤ 𝟚 ⇔ 𝟚 ×ᵤ 𝟚 ×ᵤ 𝟚
ctrlS = (id⇔ *** id⇔ *** had) >>>
        ccx >>>
        (id⇔ *** id⇔ *** had) >>>
        ccx

